OL,3,C'Gross' failings by hospital staff
OL,4,Cafter death of baby 14 hours after
OL,5,Cbirth
OL,7,FA coroner has found there were "gross"
OL,8,Fand "total and complete" failings by
OL,9,Fmedical staff at a hospital just 14
OL,10,Fhours after his birth.
OL,12,FZachary Taylor-Smith wasweighing 6
OL,13,Fpounds and 3 ounces.
OL,15,FSoon after labour, Zachary contracted
OL,16,Fan infection which led to various
OL,17,Fproblems, including breathing
OL,18,Fdifficulties.
