OL,5,Cbirth
OL,7,FHis condition began to deteriorate and
OL,8,Fhe stopped breathing. His parents say
OL,9,Fhe was then fighting for his life in
OL,10,Fthe neonatal unit at
OL,12,FBaby Zachary died aged just 14 hours
OL,13,Fold from a life-threatening condition
OL,14,Fcalled Group B Strep. The condition is
OL,15,Fa type of infection and is common for
OL,16,Fpregnant women but can be very serious
OL,17,Ffor newborn babies.
OL,19,FHowever, the inquest heard how had not
OL,20,Fbeen made aware of it until their son
OL,21,Fhad died.
