OL,7,FThe final moments of baby Zachary's
OL,8,Finquest saw Coroner Susan Evans
OL,9,Fconclude there had been "gross" and
OL,10,F"total and complete failures" in
OL,11,Frelation to basic care.
OL,13,FThe coroner also stated there had been
OL,14,Fseveral "missed opportunities" by
OL,15,Fstaff which could have prevented
OL,16,FZachary's death.
