OL,3,C'Gross' failings by hospital staff
OL,4,Cafter death of baby 14 hours after
OL,5,Cbirth
OL,7,FCoroner Evans said hospital staff
OL,8,Fshould have provided antibiotics to
OL,9,FHannah during labour and Zachary while
OL,10,Fhe was alive. If they had done so
OL,11,FZachary may have survived, she said.
OL,13,FShe added staff should have responded
OL,14,Fsooner to Zachary's deteriorated
OL,15,Fhealth on the morning of November 17,
OL,16,F2022, when risk factors were in play
OL,17,Fand should have carried out immediate
OL,18,Freviews on his condition at key points
OL,19,Fduring his short life.
