OL,7,FThe coroner said she would file a
OL,8,Freport for the prevention of future
OL,9,Fdeaths.
OL,11,FThe University Hospitals of Derby and
OL,12,FBurton NHS Foundation has fully
OL,13,Faccepted the findings of baby
OL,14,FZachary's inquest and said it is
OL,15,F"deeply sorry" for its failures in his
OL,16,Fcare before he died in November 2022
OL,17,Ffollowing breathing difficulties.
