OL,7,FIn a statement, University Hospitals
OL,8,Fof Derby and Burton NHS Trust said:
OL,9,F"The loss of a baby is devastating &
OL,10,Fwe are sincerely and deeply sorry for
OL,11,Fthe failings in Zachary's care, which
OL,12,Fwe fully accept.
OL,14,F"We should have provided antibiotics &
OL,15,Fresponded differently to changes in
OL,16,FZachary's condition.
