OL,7,F"Our thoughts very much remain with
OL,8,FHannah and Tim, who have suffered
OL,9,Fimmense pain, and we're absolutely
OL,10,Fdetermined the changes we have made
OL,11,Fwill remain embedded to improve the
OL,12,Fcare we give to babies, parents &
OL,13,Ftheir families."
OL,15,FWhat is Strep B?
OL,17,FAccording to Group B Strep Support, up
OL,18,Fto two-thirds of GBS infection in
OL,19,Fbabies are of early onset (showing
OL,20,Fwithin the first 6 days of life).
